Chairman of the Kaduna State Beach Soccer Association (KSBSA), Engr. Nimrod Musa, has inaugurated five sub-committees and association board members.
The inaugurated members are Engineer Yusuf Abubakar Mustapha (Best) vice member, Hon. Sunday O. Adeleye, Vola Abidoye (FIFA), Mohammed Sani (FIFA) Isaiah Benjamin (Media Officer), Grace John, Elder Ogbonna Daniel (WADSON) Abdullahi Isa (Technical Director) and Florence Yori (Secretary).
In his charge to the board and sub-committee members, Engr. Nimrod urged them to be prepared to make sacrifices for the upliftment of the association.
The chairman also appointed board members into various committees namely technical, training and development committee, marketing and sponsorship committee, media committee, and ethics, discipline and welfare committee.
He charged the Inaugurated board and sub-committee to make sacrifices for the upliftment of the association.
